Years back Harry would feel sad over unavoidable hate and being in the most popular boy band created so much pressure for him but look how he is now. Happy, free, radiant, and unbothered. And Lizzo, there aren’t many thicker black woman thriving in the music industry, also her dad passed away years before she became known,rip. None of that stopped her from becoming successful and getting acclaimed as a musician. These two have come a long way. They’re both shining and we’re witnessing it. They really do deserve all the love and support in the world!!!
